import React from 'react'
import {Typography,Button,Divider} from '@material-ui/core'
import {Elements,CardElement,ElementConsumer} from '@stripe/react-stripe-js'
import {loadStrip} from '@stripe/stripe-js'
import Review from './Review'
function PaymentForm(props) {
  return (
    <>
      <Review token={props.checkOutToken}/>
      <Divider/>  
      <Typography variant='h6' gutterBottom style={{margin}}>

      </Typography>
      <Button variant='outlined' color='secondary'>Back</Button>
    </>
  )
}

export default PaymentForm
